<div class="space-y-10">
  <!-- Verification Rules -->
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-3">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-indigo-50 flex items-center justify-center text-indigo-600">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
      </div>
      인증 규칙
    </h2>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <!-- Verification Method -->
      <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 9a2 2 0 012-2h.93a2 2 0 001.664-.89l.812-1.22A2 2 0 0110.07 4h3.86a2 2 0 011.664.89l.812 1.22A2 2 0 0018.07 7H19a2 2 0 012 2v9a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V9z"/><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 13a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-[10px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">인증 방식</p>
          <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-1">
            <% methods = [] %>
            <% methods << "사진 업로드" if challenge.v_photo? %>
            <% methods << "단순 체크" if challenge.v_simple? %>
            <% methods << "수치 입력" if challenge.v_metric? %>
            <% methods << "URL 공유" if challenge.v_url? %>
            <% if methods.any? %>
              <p class="font-bold text-slate-900"><%= methods.join(", ") %></p>
            <% else %>
              <p class="font-bold text-slate-900"><%= { simple: '간단 완료 체크', metric: '수치 데이터 입력', photo: '사진 업로드 인증', url: '공유 URL 링크 인증', complex: '복합형 인증' }[challenge.verification_type.to_sym] %></p>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">지정된 모든 인증을 완료해야 인정됩니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Verification Time -->
      <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-[10px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">인증 가능 시간</p>
          <p class="font-bold text-slate-900">
            <%= challenge.verification_start_time&.strftime('%H:%M') || '00:00' %> - <%= challenge.verification_end_time&.strftime('%H:%M') || '23:59' %>
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">지정된 시간 내에만 인증이 가능합니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Failure Tolerance -->
      <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-rose-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-[10px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">최대 실패 허용</p>
          <p class="font-bold text-slate-900"><%= challenge.failure_tolerance %>회까지</p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1">허용 횟수를 초과하면 챌린지에서 탈락합니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Approval Method -->
      <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-amber-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-[10px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">인증 승인 방식</p>
          <p class="font-bold text-slate-900"><%= challenge.mission_requires_host_approval ? '호스트 직접 승인' : '시스템 자동 승인' %></p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1"><%= challenge.mission_requires_host_approval ? '호스트가 인증 내용을 검토 후 최종 승인합니다.' : '인증 완료 시 즉시 인정됩니다.' %></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Re-verification -->
      <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-emerald-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-[10px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">재인증 허용</p>
          <p class="font-bold text-slate-900"><%= challenge.re_verification_allowed ? '허용' : '불가' %></p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1"><%= challenge.re_verification_allowed ? '거절 시 당일 재시도가 가능합니다.' : '거절 시 재시도가 불가능합니다.' %></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Entry Type -->
      <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-3xl border border-slate-100 flex items-start gap-4">
        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-white shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center shrink-0">
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-indigo-500" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-[10px] font-black text-slate-400 uppercase tracking-widest mb-1">참여 방식</p>
          <p class="font-bold text-slate-900"><%= challenge.admission_type_approval? ? '선별형 참여' : '자유 참여' %> | <%= challenge.is_private? ? '비공개' : '공개' %></p>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1"><%= challenge.admission_type_approval? ? '호스트의 승인이 필요합니다.' : '누구나 즉시 참여할 수 있습니다.' %></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Ranking Rules -->
  <div class="space-y-6">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-black text-slate-900 flex items-center gap-3">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-2xl bg-amber-50 flex items-center justify-center text-amber-600">
        <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2M17 16v2a2 2 0 01-2 2H9a2 2 0 01-2-2v-2m3-5v3m4-3v3m-2-6V5a2 2 0 114 0v2"/></svg>
      </div>
      순위 산정 규칙
    </h2>

    <div class="p-8 bg-slate-50 rounded-[40px] border border-slate-100 space-y-6">
      <p class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
        챌린지 종료 후 달성률이 동일한 동점자가 발생할 경우, 루틴 파인더스만의 <span class="text-indigo-600">성실도 알고리즘</span>을 통해 최종 순위가 결정됩니다.
      </p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-lg bg-indigo-600 text-white flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-black">1</span>
            <span class="text-xs font-black text-slate-900">성실도 지표</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[11px] font-medium text-slate-500 leading-relaxed pl-8">실천율 및 최대 연속 달성(Streak) 기록을 가장 우선시합니다.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-lg bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-black">2</span>
            <span class="text-xs font-black text-slate-900">활동 지표</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[11px] font-medium text-slate-500 leading-relaxed pl-8">서비스 접속률 및 커뮤니티 활동 지수를 합산하여 반영합니다.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-3">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 w-6 h-6 rounded-lg bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-600 flex items-center justify-center text-[10px] font-black">3</span>
            <span class="text-xs font-black text-slate-900">루틴 진심도</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-[11px] font-medium text-slate-500 leading-relaxed pl-8">관리 중인 개인 루틴의 개수와 전반적인 성실도를 체크합니다.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-6 border-t border-slate-200/60">
        <p class="text-[11px] font-bold text-slate-400 italic">
          * 모든 지표가 동일할 경우, 챌린지에 먼저 참여 신청을 완료한 순서(선착순)에 따라 최종 순위가 확정됩니다.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Important Notes -->
  <div class="p-8 bg-gradient-to-br from-rose-50 to-orange-50 rounded-[40px] border border-rose-100">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
      <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-xl bg-white shadow-sm flex items-center justify-center text-rose-600 shrink-0">
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <p class="text-sm font-black text-rose-900">주의사항</p>
        <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm font-medium text-slate-600">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-rose-500 mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span>챌린지 시작 후에는 규칙 변경이 불가능합니다.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-rose-500 mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span>부정 인증이 적발될 경우 즉시 탈락 처리되며, 보증금은 환급되지 않습니다.</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
            <span class="text-rose-500 mt-0.5">•</span>
            <span>챌린지 중도 탈퇴 시 보증금은 환급되지 않으며, 이미 지불한 참가비는 반환되지 않습니다.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
